## What's included

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Earth globe** | 64-segment sphere with NASA Blue Marble texture + specular map for ocean shine |
| **Atmosphere** | Custom GLSL shader producing a soft blue Fresnel glow (additive blended, back-face) |
| **Starfield** | 6,000 randomly distributed points for a space backdrop |
| **Orbit controls** | Click-drag to rotate, scroll to zoom, plus gentle auto-rotation |
| **Lighting** | Ambient fill + directional "sun" light |
| **Responsive** | Handles window resize automatically |

Open the file in any modern browser — no build step needed. The textures load from a CDN (`three-globe` package), so an internet connection is required.

