**What's included:**

- **Bed frame** — wooden base with side rails, headboard (with panel detail), footboard, and tapered legs
- **Mattress & sheet** — layered on top with a fitted sheet
- **Blanket/comforter** — draped over the lower half with a fold at the foot
- **Two pillows** — with slightly rounded edges via vertex manipulation
- **Side table & lamp** — with a working point light that has subtle flicker
- **Floor & rug** — for grounding the scene
- **Lighting** — ACES filmic tone mapping, 3-point lighting (key/fill/rim), soft shadows
- **OrbitControls** — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom, with damping

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Three.js Beetle</title>
