## What's Included

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Billboard structure** | Sign panel with metal frame, two poles, and cross-brace |
| **Canvas texture** | Custom-designed sign with gradient background, title, accent colors, and decorative elements |
| **Glow animation** | Subtle pulsing emissive glow on the sign face |
| **Environment** | Green ground, dirt road with center line, scattered trees (cone + trunk), and rocks |
| **Lighting** | Directional sun with soft shadows, hemisphere light, ambient fill, ACES filmic tone mapping |
| **Atmosphere** | Exponential fog blending into the sky color |
| **Controls** | OrbitControls with damping, polar angle clamp, and zoom limits |
| **Responsive** | Handles window resize with correct aspect ratio |

Open the file in any modern browser — no build step needed. Three.js loads from the CDN via import map.

