| **Materials** | `MeshStandardMaterial` with warm wood tones, roughness & slight metalness |
| **Lighting** | Directional key light with soft shadows, blue fill light, warm rim point light, ambient |
| **Environment** | Dark ground plane receiving shadows, floating amber particles |
| **Animation** | Gentle sinusoidal float + sway on the board, particle drift |
| **Interaction** | `OrbitControls` — drag to orbit, scroll to zoom, damped smoothing |
| **Rendering** | ACES filmic tone mapping, PCF soft shadow maps, pixel-ratio capped at 2 |

