## What's Included

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Boat Hull** | Extruded curved shape with bevel, giving a classic hull cross-section |
| **Deck & Cabin** | Box geometries with a red roof and cream walls |
| **Mast & Sails** | Cylinder mast with 3 curved sails (main, front, back) using `ShapeGeometry` |
| **Railings** | Posts and horizontal bars along the deck edges |
| **Animated Water** | Vertex-displaced plane with layered sine waves for a natural ocean look |
| **Clouds** | Clustered spheres that drift across the sky |
| **Lighting** | Directional sun (with shadows), hemisphere light, and ambient fill |
| **Boat Animation** | Gentle bobbing, rolling, and yawing on the waves |
