## What's Included

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Catenary cable** | Mathematically accurate hanging curve (`y = a·cosh(x/a)`) rendered as a tube |
| **Glowing core** | Thin emissive inner wire that pulses subtly |
| **Support poles** | Two detailed poles with cross-arms, insulators, and base plates |
| **Second cable** | Offset background cable for depth |
| **Lighting** | Directional + two colored point lights + ambient, with soft shadows |
| **Particles** | Floating dust/sparks for atmosphere |
| **Ground + grid** | Dark ground plane with subtle grid reference |
| **Orbit controls** | Click-drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |
| **Fog + tone mapping** | ACES filmic tone mapping and exponential fog for depth |

