This single HTML file renders a **3D Bactrian (two-humped) camel** with:

- **Anatomy** — body, two humps, long curved neck, head with snout/nostrils/eyes/eyelashes/ears, four legs with knees and hooves, and a tail
- **Materials** — sandy brown body, darker hooves, dark eyes, subtle nose shading
- **Environment** — sky-blue background, sandy ground plane, soft sand dunes
- **Lighting** — warm directional sunlight with soft shadows, ambient fill, and a cool-toned fill light
- **Animation** — gentle breathing (body/hump expansion), head bobbing, and tail swaying
- **Interactivity** — OrbitControls (click-drag to rotate, scroll to zoom)

