| **Carriage beam** | `BoxGeometry` | Wood |
| **Trail** | Angled `BoxGeometry` support | Wood |
| **Cross supports** | 3 vertical `BoxGeometry` pieces | Wood |
| **Wheels** (×2) | `TorusGeometry` tire + 8 spokes + hub + rim disc | Wood + iron |
