## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Cloud shape** | 12 overlapping semi-transparent spheres clustered into a fluffy form |
| **Material** | `MeshStandardMaterial` — fully rough, non-metallic, 92% opacity |
| **Lighting** | Warm directional sun + cool fill light + ambient |
| **Animation** | Gentle vertical bobbing, subtle yaw/roll, and per-puff "breathing" scale |
| **Atmosphere** | Sky-blue background + exponential fog for depth |
| **Responsive** | Handles window resize automatically |

