window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
  camera.aspect = innerWidth / innerHeight;
  camera.updateProjectionMatrix();
  renderer.setSize(innerWidth, innerHeight);
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **C-frame** | Back spine + top/bottom arms built from boxes |
| **Fixed jaw** | Bottom jaw with grip-face plate |
| **Threaded screw** | Cylinder wrapped with torus rings simulating threads |
| **Movable jaw** | Slides up/down on the screw rod |
| **T-handle** | Red grip handles on top for turning |
| **Slider control** | Bottom of screen — drag to open/close the clamp |
| **Lighting** | Directional + rim + ambient with soft shadows |
| **Interaction** | Orbit (drag), zoom (scroll), pan (right-drag) via `OrbitControls` |

