## What's in the scene

| Component | Geometry | Details |
|---|---|---|
| **Desk** | Flat box | Dark surface, receives shadows |
| **Monitor** | Bezel + screen plane | Canvas-textured "code editor" display with syntax highlighting and blinking cursor |
| **Keyboard** | Base + 48 key boxes | 4×12 grid of small key caps |
| **Mouse** | Box + glowing button | Positioned to the right of the keyboard |
| **Tower** | Vertical box + fan + LED strip | Pulsing blue fan glow on the front panel |

## Features

- **OrbitControls** — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom, right-drag to pan
- **Shadows** — PCF soft shadow maps from a key light
- **Three-point lighting** — key (white), fill (blue), rim (warm)
- **ACES tone mapping** for cinematic contrast
- **Live screen** — a `<canvas>` texture redraws every frame with fake code, a blinking cursor, and an elapsed-time counter
- **Responsive** — handles window resizing

