## What's in the scene

| Element | Details |
|---|---|
| **Two curtain panels** | Custom GLSL shaders create multi-frequency sine-wave folds with gravity tapering and animated swaying |
| **Curtain rod** | Metallic cylinder with sphere finials at each end |
| **Window frame** | Dark box-geometry frame behind the curtains with a soft pulsing glow |
| **Lighting** | 5-point setup — rect area light (window), directional key/fill, point rim, and ambient |
| **Shadows** | PCF soft shadow map from the key light |
| **Orbit controls** | Drag to orbit, scroll to zoom around the curtain |

