|---|---|
| **Proximal phalanx** | Tapered cylinder from knuckle → PIP joint |
| **Middle phalanx** | Tapered cylinder from PIP → DIP joint |
| **Distal phalanx** | Tapered cylinder from DIP → fingertip |
| **3 Joint bumps** | Scaled spheres at knuckle, PIP, DIP |
| **Fingertip cap** | Half-sphere capping the tip |
| **Fingernail** | Partial sphere on the dorsal surface |
| **Crease lines** | Thin torus segments at joint creases |
| **Lighting** | Hemisphere + key/fill/rim three-point setup |
| **Animation** | Subtle idle sway for a "living" feel |
| **Interaction** | OrbitControls — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |

Open the file in any modern browser — no build step needed. Everything loads from jsDelivr CDN.

